OL,3,CMan accused of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cpolice officer remanded in custody
OL,6,FA man has been remanded in custody
OL,7,Fafter appearing in court accused of
OL,8,Fthe attempted murder of a police
OL,9,Fofficer in Downpatrick last weekend.
OL,11,FIt comes after a stolen police car was
OL,12,Fdriven at the officer during an
OL,13,Fincident in Colmcille Road in the Co
OL,14,FDown town on Sunday which was
OL,15,Fcondemned by Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,16,FStarmer as a "horrific incident".
OL,26,@xD@NOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
