OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780665075
OL,3,CMan accused of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cpolice officer remanded in custody
OL,6,FOn Thursday morning, Downpatrick
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court heard that the
OL,8,Fofficer remains in hospital, and is
OL,9,F"seriously unwell", having sustained a
OL,10,Fbroken wrist, a crush injury to a leg
OL,11,Fwhich they cannot put weight on,
OL,12,Finjuries to the head, cuts and
OL,13,Fabrasions, and is in "a great deal of
OL,14,Fpain".
OL,16,FConor Carey, 36, of Glassheena Road in
OL,17,FDownpatrick, appeared in court.
OL,19,FHe has been charged with attempted
OL,20,Fmurder in relation to the incident.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@RO]uD@VOUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780665075
OL,3,CMan accused of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cpolice officer remanded in custody
OL,6,FCarey is also charged with aggravated
OL,7,Fvehicle taking causing injury on the
OL,8,Fsame date and driving without
OL,9,Finsurance.
OL,11,FHe replied "yes" when asked whether he
OL,12,Funderstood the charges.
OL,14,FA detective sergeant said he can
OL,15,Fconnect the accused to the charges.
OL,17,FA defence lawyer for Carey said his
OL,18,Fclient "strenuously denies any
OL,19,Finvolvement in the matter".
OL,26,@sD@LOUsD@PO]zD@HOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
