PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780665075
OL,3,CMan accused of attempted murder of
OL,4,Cpolice officer remanded in custody
OL,6,FHe said there would be no application
OL,7,Ffor bail at this stage, but may be in
OL,8,Fthe near future.
OL,10,FThe case was adjourned to June 18.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, on Monday, Kieran Turley,
OL,13,F27, from Vianstown Road in
OL,14,FDownpatrick, appeared before the
OL,15,Ftown's magistrates' court charged with
OL,16,Fdangerous driving, driving while
OL,17,Fdisqualified and using a motor vehicle
OL,18,Fwith no insurance.
OL,20,FHe was remanded in custody to appear
OL,21,Fin court again later in June.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
